

**Matsh g Paul ab wo i gei si geꞌe kownal wui **

1 Sh am d i waik tash amjed mat am i dahiwua g Festus Cesaria t am, tsh gam hu hih Jerusalem wui. 2-3 Tsh ab wui i hihi g uꞌugchu papal ch geꞌeged hemajkam k am ahgid hegai mo haschu ab i chum abchud g Paul ch ab si tahni mat ab wo i bei Jerusalem wui. Kush eda idam am heki hu e aꞌaga mat wo mua g Paul mat ab wo uꞌad. 

4 Sh hab kaij g Festus, “Am o d wabsh kia lihso Cesaria t am. Nt eda hemuch am uhpam wo hih. 5 Kumt am haꞌi wo ni‑oid k am wo ah mam haschu ab abchud.” 

6 K am dakahim g Festus am hu i hemako domig k gam hu hahawa hih Cesaria wui. T hegam geꞌeged hemajkam gam hu ep hihi. 

Baꞌich i tash at am i dahiwua g Festus lodaita kih ch ed k am ha chehani mat am wo i wahki g Paul. 7 T am i wahki. T an wehgaj gegokiwua k ab ha hekaj si pi ap haꞌichu abchud ch wabshaba pi e nako mas wo wohokamch ihda. 

8 T g Paul am e wehhejed neok k hab kaij, “Pi ant haꞌichu shaꞌi pi ap hab juh manis melchkwua g t‑chehanig ahchim Tutuligo k pi shaꞌi uamhu g geꞌe cheopi k pi ab hu shaꞌi wui kehk g kownal.” 

9 K hab kaij g Festus ab wui, “Pt hig am wo hih Jerusalem wui mant am haꞌab wo m‑lodai.” Bo kaij no pi hab elid mat wo s‑hohhoꞌi g Tutuligo. 

10 K hab kaij g Paul, “Ia ani kehk kownal lodaita kih ed mant ia haꞌab wo chum ni‑lodaitach. Am ap wa si s‑mahch mant pi haꞌichu am hu hab shaꞌi juh mas pi apꞌe am ha wui g ni‑wehm oꞌodham. 11 Pi ant ab hu wo em‑tai mams wabsh wo ni‑dagito matp hab wo sha mahsk mant mul g chehanig. M o wa s‑apꞌe mamt wabsh wo ni‑muhkid mantp am hugkam mul. K wabshaba pi woho hegai mo ab ni‑abchud. T heg hekaj pi hedai wo e nako mas ab wo i ni‑dagito ha wui. Ab ant wui wo i gei g si uhgchu kownal.” Neh, bo kaij g Paul. 

12 K eda am dadha hegam mo am haꞌichu i shelamid ch am aꞌaga ihda. K g Festus ab ha kahk ch hab hahawa kaij ab Paul wui, “Neh, pt hemho wa am wo e uꞌapa si uhgchu kownal wui napt pi ab wui i gei.” 

**Matsh g Agrippa ch Bernice am kaiha g Paul **

13 K am hu hebai hema d kownal ch hab chehgig Agrippa. Sh g uwi wehngaj hab chehgig Bernice. Tsh idam am chehgio g Festus noki pi s‑ap ab i neid. 

14 Sh am heꞌekia i tash amjed, sh am ha ahgid g Festus ab amjed g Paul ch hab kaij, “Ia o hema kuhpi g oꞌodham ch hab chehgig Paul. T g Felix pi i wuhshad. 15 Kunt wa am hih Jerusalem wui k am ha nei g Tutuligo uꞌugchu papal ch geꞌeged. K hegam ab haꞌichu abchud ihda lihso ch ab ni‑chehani mant wo mua. 16 Ni wabshaba am ha ahgid mo pi hab mahs g t‑kownalig chehanig. T hemho wa wehpeg am wo i e hudaw g lihso ha wehm hegam mo ab haꞌichu abchud k am wo neo e wehhejed. T g kownal ab haha wo mah g namkidadgaj. 

17 “T wa woho i dada hegam Tutuligo ha wanimeddam. Nt am ha hekaj dahiwua kownal daikud ed mant wo ha kaiha. Kumt ab i wahki g lihso. 18 T am gegokiwua hegam mo ab haꞌichu chum abchud. Kuni hab ni‑ahg matp hems geꞌe haꞌichu ab wo abch ab t‑chehanig amjed. 19 K wabshaba ab wabsh e‑himdag amjed ab haꞌichu neꞌowin ch heg amjed ehp oꞌodham mash hab chehgig Jesus ch atsh heki hu muh. K eda g Paul hab kaij mat uhpam e chegito. 

20 “Nt am wabsh i pi ni‑amich mant has masma si tasho haꞌichu wo s‑mai ab amjed k heg hekaj ab kakke g Paul mas wo s‑hohhoꞌi mat am uhpam wo hih Jerusalem wui k ab haꞌab wo e lodaitach. 21 K wabshaba ab t‑ahgid g Paul mat ab wo i gei si geꞌe kownal wui mat heg am wo mamche hegai mo haschu ab i abchud. Nt wa woho am ha cheha g shondal mat wo si nuhkud k ab wo ai mat am wo e uꞌapa si geꞌe kownal wui.” 22 Kush hab kaij g Agrippa am Festus wui, “Ahni ani hab waꞌap chum s‑kaimk ihda oꞌodham.” 

Sh hab kaij g Festus, “Pt wo wa kah siꞌalim.” 

23 K am baꞌich d i tash, t hab masma i ha wahpki g Festus mo d si s‑has hahaꞌichu idam Agrippa ch Bernice. K hegam ep ha wehmaj mo d si uꞌugchu shondal ha‑geꞌegeꞌejig ch hegam mo d si s‑has hahaꞌichu heg eda kihhim. Kumt am i wahki g Paul. 24 K g Festus hab hahawa kaij: 

“Ahpi Agrippa map d kownal ch ahpim s‑has hahaꞌichu oꞌodham, m ia kehk em‑wui ihda oꞌodham. K g Tutuligo iia kch ab Jerusalem t ab ab haꞌichu abchud ab ni‑wui ch am si e gewpkad mat hemho wa wo e mua. 25 Nt wabshaba pi shaꞌi cheh g chuꞌijigaj mas heg hekaj wo e muhkid. 

“K heg wa hejel hab kaij mat ab wo i gei si geꞌe kownal wui. T hekaj hemho wa am hab wo e juh. 26-27 Ni wabshaba pi ni‑amichud mant haschu am wo oꞌohani g si geꞌe kownal ab amjed. K pi hab chum mahs mas am wo e uꞌapa g lihso pi am hu tasho ahgk mas haschu d chuꞌijigaj. Nt heg hekaj ia uꞌapa em‑wui mamt am wo i kaiha, wahm ahpi Agrippa map d kownal. Ntp hems haha wo s‑mai ab em‑amjed mant haschu am wo oꞌoha.” 

